{
  "text": "The Maximum Flow Community (MFC) algorithm [CITATION_1] , the Girvan-Newman algorithm (GN) [CITATION_2] and its improvements [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] , the Hyperlink Induced Topic Search algorithm (HITS) [CITATION_5] , the Wu-Huberman algorithm (WH) [CITATION_6] and the Clique Percolation Method (CPM) [CITATION_7] are typical heuristic based algorithms for solving NCMPs.",
  "correct_citation": {
